==Standings==
{{2026 FIFA World Cup group tables|Group A}}

In the [[2026 FIFA World Cup knockout stage#Round of 32|round of 32]]:<ref name="regulations"/>
* The winner of Group A will advance to play the third-placed team of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group C|Group C]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group E|Group E]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group F|Group F]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group H|Group H]], or [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group I|Group I]].
* The runner-up of Group A will advance to play the runner-up of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group B|Group B]].
* The third-placed team of Group A might advance to play the winner of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group E|Group E]] or [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group G|Group G]] (if one of the [[2026 FIFA World Cup#Ranking of third-placed teams|eight best third-placed teams]] from the group stage).

