===Mexico vs South Africa===
The two teams have faced each other four times, most recently in a [[2010 FIFA World Cup Group A#South Africa vs Mexico|1–1]] draw in the [[2010 FIFA World Cup]] [[List of FIFA World Cup opening matches|opening match]], with South Africa as the host nation.<ref>{{cite web|title=Mexico national football team: record v South Africa |url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/mexico/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/South%20Africa|website=11v11.com|access-date=December 5, 2025}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mexico vs. South Africa Head-to-Head in the World Cups|url=https://www.thesoccerworldcups.com/head_to_head/mexico_vs_south_africa.php|website=thesoccerworldcups.com|access-date=December 5, 2025}}</ref> This match coincidentally will take place exactly 16 years after.

