===Mexico vs South Korea===
The sides have previously met 15 times including twice in the World Cup, with Mexico winning both matches: [[1998 FIFA World Cup Group E#South Korea vs Mexico|3–1]] in the [[1998 FIFA World Cup|1998 tournament]] in France, and [[2018 FIFA World Cup Group F#South Korea vs Mexico|2–1]] in the [[2018 FIFA World Cup|2018 edition]] in Russia. Their most recent meeting was a 2–2 draw in 2025.<ref>{{cite web|title=Mexico national football team: record v South Korea|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/mexico/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Korea%20Republic|website=11v11.com|access-date=December 5, 2025}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mexico vs. South Korea Head-to-Head in the World Cups|url=https://www.thesoccerworldcups.com/head_to_head/mexico_vs_south_korea.php|website=thesoccerworldcups.com|access-date=December 5, 2025}}</ref>

