===Czech Republic vs Mexico===
The teams only played each other once in 2000, a 2–1 win for the Czechs.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/czech-republic/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Mexico/|title=Czech Republic national football team: record v Mexico|website=www.11v11.com}}</ref> Czech Republic predecessor country Czechoslovakia played Mexico at the [[1962 World Cup]] in a game in which Czechoslovakia scored after just 15 seconds, the second fastest goal in World Cup history, however Mexico came back to win [[1962 FIFA World Cup Group 3#Mexico vs Czechoslovakia|3–1]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/mexico/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Czechoslovakia/|title=Mexico national football team: record v Czechoslovakia|website=www.11v11.com}}</ref>
